To cite Aboria in publications, please use:

Robinson, M., & Bruna, M. (2017). Particle-based and meshless methods with Aboria. SoftwareX, 6, 172-178.

https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S2352711017300250

A BibTeX entry for LaTeX users is

@article{robinson2017particle,
  title={Particle-based and meshless methods with Aboria},
  author={Robinson, Martin and Bruna, Maria},
  journal={SoftwareX},
  volume={6},
  pages={172--178},
  year={2017},
  publisher={Elsevier}
}

